.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGot%20a%20question%20for%20our%20columnist%3F%20Write%20to%20For%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%20using%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdhFnAxR57cNtGiwNUd-6vLAYAc75grvly3C10-854vFP4arw%2Fviewform%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20Google%20form%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EDear%20For%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20husband%20grew%20up%20poor.%20He%20missed%20meals%2C%20wore%20shoes%20until%20they%20fell%20off%20his%20feet%2C%20and%20went%20without%20electricity%20until%20his%20family%20could%20afford%20the%20bill.%20He%20was%20the%20kind%20of%20poor%20that%2C%20growing%20up%20middle%20class%2C%20I%20thought%20only%20existed%20in%20movies.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENow%2C%20he's%20a%20salesman%2C%20and%20I'm%20a%20teacher.%20We%20have%20three%20kids%2C%20and%20we%20get%20by.%20We've%20always%20had%20enough%2C%20even%20when%20it%20gets%20tight.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20have%20financial%20goals%20and%20try%20to%20set%20aside%20money%20for%20our%20retirement.%20The%20problem%20is%20that%20my%20husband%20always%20wants%20to%20put%20those%20financial%20goals%20ahead%20of%20the%20well-being%20of%20our%20family.%20He%20tries%20to%20institute%20rules%20like%20monthly%20grocery%20budgets%20that%20allow%20us%20to%20put%20more%20money%20in%20savings%2C%20and%20if%20we%20run%20out%20of%20food%20for%20the%20month%2C%20we%20go%20without.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20I've%20gone%20out%20of%20town%20while%20he%20stayed%20home%20with%20the%20kids%2C%20and%20he's%20bragged%20about%20how%20they%20didn't%20grocery%20shop%20once%2C%20even%20after%20they%20ran%20out%20of%20food%2C%20forcing%20the%20kids%20to%20tough%20it%20out%20and%20make%20do.%20I%20was%20appalled%2C%20but%20he%20saw%20it%20as%20an%20achievement.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20don't%20want%20our%20kids%20to%20experience%20the%20kind%20of%20deprivation%20he%20did.%20I%20don't%20think%20he%20does%20either%2C%20as%20he%20remembers%20it%20being%20traumatic%20for%20him%20and%20his%20siblings%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20seems%20to%20believe%20it%20builds%20character%2C%20and%20our%20kids%20need%20the%20same%20struggle.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EMostly%2C%20I%20have%20been%20able%20to%20set%20the%20standard%20for%20our%20family%2C%20but%20it%20has%20led%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20conflict%20over%20where%20our%20financial%20goals%20rank%20on%20the%20priority%20list.%20How%20do%20I%20talk%20to%20him%20about%20this%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESincerely%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrustrated%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDear%20Frustrated%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20parents%2C%20we%20want%20to%20eliminate%20as%20much%20pain%2C%20hardship%2C%20and%20risk%20as%20possible%20from%20our%20children's%20lives.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20know%20kids%20need%20hardship%20and%20risk%20to%20grow%20into%20adults%20who%20can%20overcome%20obstacles%20with%20grace%20and%20determination.%20So%2C%20while%20I%20understand%20where%20your%20husband%20is%20coming%20from%2C%20I%20also%20don't%20think%20it's%20safe%20or%20acceptable%20to%20let%20your%20kids%20go%20hungry%20because%20your%20monthly%20grocery%20budget%20is%20blown.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERecognizing%20your%20husband's%20intent%20is%20your%20best%20bet%20for%20getting%20on%20the%20same%20page.%20Not%20to%20make%20your%20marriage%20too%20corporate%2C%20but%20scheduling%20regular%20strategy%20meetings%20with%20your%20husband%20to%20discuss%20your%20hopes%20for%20your%20kids%20and%20how%20you%20each%20want%20to%20get%20there%20will%20create%20an%20excellent%20opportunity%20for%20you%20to%20show%20him%20that%20you%20have%20the%20same%20values%20for%20your%20kids%20that%20he%20does%20and%20allow%20you%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20mutually%20agreeable%20plan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20there%20is%20another%20side%20to%20your%20husband's%20tendency%20toward%20deprivation%2C%20and%20that%20is%20the%20financial%20savings%20that%20occur%20every%20time%20you%20eliminate%20spending%20%E2%80%94%20even%20when%20it's%20essential.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETraditional%20budgets%20don't%20leave%20much%20wiggle%20room%2C%20so%20when%20anything%20changes%2C%20it's%20stressful%20to%20see%20your%20budget%20breakdown%20every%20time%20the%20price%20of%20eggs%20goes%20up.%20If%20you're%20worried%20about%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fbest-retirement-plans%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eretirement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20temptation%20is%20to%20simply%20not%20let%20this%20happen.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECutting%20the%20food%20budget%20seems%20easy%2C%20because%20while%20we%20must%20eat%20to%20survive%2C%20the%20quality%20and%20even%20the%20quantity%20are%20negotiable.%20Clothing%20budgets%20offer%20the%20same%20flexibility%2C%20and%20extracurriculars%20like%20sports%20and%20music%20are%20voluntary%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20them%20at%20all.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20general%2C%20if%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20flex%20your%20overall%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fbest-budgeting-apps%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebudget%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20squeezing%20grocery%2C%20clothing%2C%20and%20extracurriculars%20can%20feel%20like%20the%20best%20solution.%2