mostly%20set%20the%20standard%26quot%3B%20for%20your%20family%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20reason%20for%20that%20to%20change.%20Second%2C%20recognize%20that%20he%20isn't%20entirely%20wrong.%20Your%20kids%20can%20go%20without%20some%20things.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20where%20those%20parenting%20strategy%20meetings%20come%20in.%20Set%20up%20an%20allowance%20system%20that%20makes%20your%20kids%20work%20for%20their%20indulgences.%20Don't%20say%20yes%20to%20everything%3B%20whether%20it's%20no%20to%20the%20drive-thru%20when%20it's%20cheaper%20to%20pack%20a%20lunch%20or%20no%20to%20building%20a%20name-brand%20sneaker%20collection%20for%20them%2C%20allow%20them%20to%20experience%20not%20getting%20everything%20they%20want.%20You%20can%20save%20money%20on%20your%20kids%20and%20build%20their%20characters%20while%20you%20do%20it%2C%20but%20to%20your%20point%2C%20this%20doesn't%20mean%20prioritizing%20your%20retirement%20over%20their%20basic%20needs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESit%20down%20with%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fhow-to-find-financial-advisor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efinancial%20planner%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20your%20husband%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20sustainable%20blueprint%20that%20will%20put%20you%20on%20track%20for%20financial%20security%20after%20you%20leave%20the%20workforce.%20Having%20a%20plan%20and%20seeing%20a%20positive%20financial%20forecast%20should%20give%20your%20husband%20the%20peace%20of%20mind%20he%20needs%20to%20stop%20squirreling%20away%20every%20spare%20cent%20for%20a%20scary%2C%20unknown%20future.%20This%20will%20allow%20him%20to%20rest%20in%20the%20financial%20security%20you've%20built%20together%20and%20are%20now%20giving%20your%20children.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERooting%20for%20you%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp