%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20long%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Dr%20Mehta%20said%20he%20put%20his%20Apple%20Watch%20in%20the%20tray%20during%20the%20security%20check.%20%26quot%3BThe%20moment%20I%20crossed%20security%2C%20I%20started%20putting%20things%20back%20into%20my%20laptop%20bag.%20I%20could%20feel%20that%20something%20is%20missing%20%26amp%3B%20I%20realised%20I%20don't%20have%20my%20watch.%20I%20asked%20the%20CISF%20guy%20standing%20there.%20He%20asked%20me%20to%20look%20again%20in%20my%20bag%2C%20pocket%20etc%20which%20I%20had%20already%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20turned%20around%20curiously%20%26amp%3B%20saw%20someone%20looking%20back%20at%20me%20while%20walking%20away.%20I%20didn't%20care%20about%20what%20CISF%20guy%20was%20about%20to%20do%20or%20say%20%26amp%3B%20started%20walking%20for%20that%20guy.%20Few%20steps%20ahead%20I%20saw%20him%20standing%20at%20the%20%40titanwatches%20Helios%20store%20on%20the%20left%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Mehta%20said%20in%20his%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESomething%20strange%20%26amp%3B%20shocking%20happened%20today.%20I%20was%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDelhiAirport%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40DelhiAirport%3C%2Fa%3E%20T3%20a%20while%20ago%20at%20the%20security.%20I%20had%20put%20my%20Apple%20Watch%20in%20the%20tray%20for%20security%20check.%20The%20moment%20I%20crossed%20security%2C%20I%20started%20putting%20things%20back%20into%20my%20laptop%20bag.%20I%20could%20feel%20that%20something%20is%20missing%20%26amp%3B%20I%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Dr%20Tushar%20Mehta%20(%40dr_tushar_mehta)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdr_tushar_mehta%2Fstatus%2F1883089757850210373%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2025%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20confronted%20him%20%26amp%3B%20forcibly%