3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20went%20to%20my%20local%20Chili's%20to%20check%20out%20the%20vibes%20and%20taste%20the%20viral%20menu%20items.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20a%20tough%20few%20years%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20food%20chains.%20One%20that%20seems%20to%20be%20bucking%20the%20trend%20is%20Chili's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20went%20along%20on%20a%20Friday%20night%20with%20my%20best%20friend%20to%20see%20who%20was%20eating%20at%20one%20of%20their%20restaurants%20in%20Queen's%2C%20NY%2C%20what%20they%20seemed%20to%20be%20ordering%2C%20and%20what%20the%20vibes%20were%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20found%20was%20that%20Chili's%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20go-to%20for%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20families%2C%20sports%20fans%2C%20and%20friends%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20weekend.%20And%20me%2C%20a%2024-year-old%20writer%20from%20Houston.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20disclaimer%2C%20I'm%20somewhat%20of%20a%20regular%20at%20Chili's%2C%20so%20I%20know%20my%20way%20around%20the%20menu.%20I%20hadn't%20been%20on%20a%20popular%20weekend%20night%2C%20however%2C%20and%20I%20was%20surprised%20at%20how%20busy%20it%20was.%20We%20didn't%20mind%20because%20this%20location%20is%20situated%20in%20a%20strip%20mall%20where%20we%20could%20kill%20time%20strolling%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrinker%20International%2C%20the%20parent%20company%20of%20Chili's%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finvestors.brinker.com%2Fstatic-files%2Ff910e95d-5993-4a1d-81b6-ac67a7e0d441%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ereported%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%207.4%25%20increase%20in%20same-store%20sales%20at%20Chili's%20for%202024%2C%20and%20sales%20jumped%2014%25%20on%20the%20same%20basis%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%20fiscal%202025%2C%20which%20ended%20in%20September%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20uptick%20in%20sales%20seemed%20to%20be%20reflected%20at%20our%20restaurant.%20We%20walked%20into%20a%20packed%20host%20area%20with%20patrons%20in%20line%20to%20be%20seated%20and%20a%20wait%20time%20of%2045%20minutes%20to%20an%20hour%20at%209%20p.m.%20%E2%80%94%20something%20I'd%20expect%20more%20from%20a%20trendy%20restaurant%20in%20Manhattan.%20The%20other%20food%20options%20in%20the%20area%20were%20mostly%20fast-casual%20with%20limited%20seating%2C%20save%20for%20California%20Pizza%20Kitchen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20we%20were%20seated%20(in%20less%20than%2045%20minutes)%2C%20we%20immediately%20ordered%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchilis-got-gen-z-attention-social-media-restaurant-meal-deals-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eviral%20Triple%20Dipper%20appetizer%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20new%20to%20Chili's%2C%20the%20Triple%20Dipper%20is%20a%20sampler%20of%20appetizers%20that%20can%20be%20customized%20to%20your%20preferences%20for%20under%20%2420.%20We%20chose%20the%20cheeseburger%20sliders%2C%20chicken%20tenders%2C%20and%20egg%20rolls%20for%20our%20three%20selections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222217%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Triple%20Dipper%20menu%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6793fc1aeb4be2fff9a21b6b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221732%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20Triple%20Dipper%20came%20out%20to%20%2417.29.%3Cp%3EJordan%20Hart%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Triple%20Dipper%20has%20gained%20a%20following%20online%2C%20with%20TikTokers%20showing%20anything%20from%20cheese%20pulls%20(a%20video%20of%20the%20epic%20stretchy%20string%20of%20cheese%20from%20mozzarella%20sticks)%20to%20first-timers%20filming%20themselves%20trying%20the%20options.%20These%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchilis-value-meals-deals-3-for-me-triple-dipper-staying-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evalue%20meals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20we%20wrote%20about%20late%20last%20year%2C%20are%20helping%20the%20restaurant%20chain%20grow%2C%20Chili's%20CMO%20George%20Felix%20said%2C%20and%20they're%20not%20going%20anywhere%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20we%20overheard%20the%20table%20next%20to%20us%20telling%20the%20server%20that%20it%20was%20their%20first%20time%20at%20Chili's%2C%20and%20they%20ordered%20a%20Triple%20Dipper%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20our%20drinks%2C%20we%20chose%20the%20%26quot%3BMarg%20of%20the%20Month%26quot%3B%3A%20a%20%246%20margarita%20called%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Resolution%20Breaker.%26quot%3B%20It's%20made%20with%20tequila%2C%20pineapple%20juice%2C%20fresh%20sour%2C%20mango%20syrup%2C%20and%20Sprite.%20The%20price%20for%20a%20cocktail%20seemed%20pretty%20reasonable%20compared%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20places%20in%20the%20five%20boroughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Resolution%20Break%20Margarita%20menu%20item%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6793f96f4bf52b7bab8a6742%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChili's%20offers%20a%20specialty%20drink%20every%20month.%3Cp%3EJordan%20Hart%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20other%20eateries%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20bring%20customers%20back%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-chilis-versus-tgi-fridays-bankruptcy-filing-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epromotional%20deals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Chili's%20has%20been%20building%20momentum.%20Alongside%20the%20%26quot%3BTriple%20Dipper%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchilis-value-meals-deals-3-for-me-triple-dipper-staying-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E3%20For%20Me%26quot%3B%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20offers%20an%20appetizer%2C%20entr%C3%A9e%2C%20and%20drink%20starting%20at%20%2410.99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20best%20friend%20went%20for%20that%20but%20upgraded%20to%20the%20six-ounce%20sirloin%20for%20%2416.99%2C%20with%20chips%20and%20salsa%20as%20her%20appetizer.%20I%20decided%20to%20get%20a%20Chili's%20classic%20that%20I%20hadn't%20had%20in%20years%3A%20the%20baby%20back%20ribs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilar%20to%20the%20%26quot%3B3%20For%20Me%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BTriple%20Dipper%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%26quot%3BSmokehouse%20Combo%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20customizable%20plate%20of%20barbecue%20and%20sides.%20I%20got%20two%20proteins%20and%20two%20sides%20for%20%2422.49%2C%20which%20I%20enjoyed%20%E2%80%94%20but%20saved%20some%20for%20home.%20I%20barely%20touched%20the%20ribs%20by%20the%20time%20I'd%20finished%20off%20my%20portion%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BTriple%20Dipper%26quot%3B%20and%20our%20chips%20and%20salsa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chili's%20smokehouse%20combo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6793fce8eb4be2fff9a21ba8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20%26quot%3BSmokehouse%20Combo%26quot%3B%20came%20with%20barbecue%20ribs%20and%20sausage%20(not%20pictured).%3Cp%3EJordan%20Hart%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20stayed%20until%20the%20last%20call%20at%20the%20bar%2C%20around%2010%3A30%20p.m.%20The%20dining%20room%20stayed%20packed%20throughout%20our%20hour-and-a-half%20dinner.%20I%20observed%20families%2C%20people%20just%20hanging%20out%20at%20the%20bar%20watching%20sports%2C%20and%20a%20few%20girls-night-out%20tables%2C%20like%20us.%20Servers%20circulated%20around%20the%20dining%20room%20nonstop%2C%20it%20seemed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20total%20check%20came%20out%20to%20just%20under%20%24100.%20We%20had%20two%20alcoholic%20drinks%20each%2C%20two%20appetizers%2C%20and%20two%20entr%C3%A9es%2C%20so%20not%20a%20bad%20deal%20by%20New%20York%20standards.%20I'll%20definitely%20be%20back%20for%20another%20%26quot%3BTriple%20Dipper%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20I%20think%20I'll%20stick%20to%20weeknights%20to%20avoid%20the%20crowds%20and%20focus%20on%20my%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwent-to-chilis-ordered-triple-dipper-having-moment-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737887462000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6793e5c3e7e163809a227874%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwent-to-chilis-ordered-triple-dipper-having-moment-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chili's%20%26quot%3BTriple%20Dipper%26quot%3B%20appetizer%20and%20%26quot%3B3%20For%20Me%26quot%3B%20deals%20are%20having%20a%20moment%20online.%20I%20went%20to%20see%20who%20was%20eating%20on%20a%20Friday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jhart%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Hart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwent-to-chilis-ordered-triple-dipper-having-moment-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22To%20fight%20air%20pollution%2C%20Thailand%20makes%20public%20rides%20free%20for%20a%20week%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737887414000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117577266%2Cimgsize-1410167.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fto-fight-air-pollution-thailand-makes-public-rides-free-for-a-week%2Farticleshow%2F117577190.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F117577190.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThailand%20has%20introduced%20free%20public%20transport%20in%20Bangkok%20for%20a%20week%20to%20tackle%20severe%20air%20pollution.%20Over%20350%20schools%20were%20closed%20due%20to%20hazardous%20PM2.5%20levels.%20The%20government%20also%20banned%20crop%20stubble%20burning%20and%20implemented%20work-from-home%20schemes%20to%20improve%20the%20city's%20air%20quality.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Des