usinessinsider.com%2Fcostco-shareholders-reject-anti-dei-proposal-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannual%20meeting%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20your%20plan%20to%20address%20lack%20of%20adequate%20parking%20in%20your%20warehouses%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVachris%20said%20that%20some%20options%20include%20buying%20nearby%20land%20to%20add%20space%20or%20building%20upper-level%20parking%20on%20top%20of%20some%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20full%20parking%20lots%20generally%20mean%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-city-vs-suburbs-differences-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebusy%20warehouses%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20that's%20where%20a%20more%20recent%20trend%20has%20been%20emerging%20for%20the%20company%3A%20just%20add%20a%20whole%20new%20warehouse%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVachris%20said%20the%20company%20refers%20to%20the%20move%20as%20%26quot%3Bcannibalizing%20these%20buildings%20to%20take%20some%20pressure%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-costco-warehouses-opening-us-cities-march-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECostco's%20most%20recent%20openings%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20in%20Pleasanton%2C%20California%20%E2%80%94%20is%20exactly%20this%20sort%20of%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20location%20sits%20between%20three%20older%20high-volume%20warehouses%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%20and%20still%20managed%20to%20do%20the%20highest-ever%20US%20opening%20day%20sales%20for%20the%20company%2C%20with%20a%20whopping%20%242.9%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20so-called%20in-fill%20locations%20are%20an%20increasingly%20important%20piece%20of%20Costco's%20growth%20strategy%2C%20execs%20have%20said%20on%20earnings%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20May%2C%20Vachris%20said%20eight%20locations%20were%20opening%20that%20year%20that%20initially%20cannibalized%20existing%20Costco%20warehouses.%20That%20accounts%20for%20about%20a%20t