20spent%20a%20decade%20in%20the%20corporate%20world%2C%20working%20at%20large%20firms%20like%20Dropbox%20and%20smaller%20startups%2C%20before%20calling%20it%20quits%20to%20work%20for%20himself%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20point%2C%20he'd%20experimented%20with%20side%20hustles%20for%20years.%20His%20first%20attempt%20at%20making%20money%20on%20the%20side%20was%20an%20e-commerce%20business%20selling%20sampler%20tea%20boxes.%20He%20was%20living%20in%20San%20Francisco%20at%20the%20time%20and%20working%20at%20Dropbox%20as%20a%20product%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20learned%20a%20lot%20about%2C%20OK%2C%20what%20is%20it%20actually%20like%20to%20build%20something%20on%20the%20side%3F%26quot%3B%20Zhuang%2C%2033%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20also%20learned%20that%20e-commerce%20wasn't%20something%20that%20I%20was%20particularly%20interested%20in%20doing%20a%20lot%20of%20afterward.%20I%20would%20say%20it%20didn't%20work%20out%2C%20but%20it%20was%20a%20good%20lesson%20learned%20for%20future%20side%20hustles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20quit%20Dropbox%20in%202018%20to%20take%20a%20yearlong%20travel%20sabbatical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20much%20of%20my%20life%20up%20until%20that%20point%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20had%20been%20a%20chronic%20high%20achiever%20of%20sorts.%20I%20had%20grinded%20hard%20in%20my%20career%20to%20pursue%20what%20I%20thought%20was%20my%20definition%20of%20success%20at%20the%20time%3A%20to%20become%20a%20high-paying%20tech%20executive%20or%20the%20founder%20of%20a%20unicorn%20startup%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhuang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Dropbox%20went%20public%20in%202018%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20like%20I%20had%20'made%20it'%20to%20some%20extent.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20had%20checked%20off%20a%20milestone%20that%20was%20important%20to%20me%2C%20but%20I%20felt%20burned%20out%2C%20and%20I%20struggled%20to%20decide%20what%20I%20actually%20wanted%20to%20do%20next.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221445%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22dexter%20zhuang%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679406e7196626c4098500bb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221084%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZhuang%20met%20his%20wife%20while%20traveling%20the%20world.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Dexter%20Zhuang%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20decided%20to%20tap%20into%20some%20of%20his%20savings%20and%20live%20out%20a%20dream%20that%20he'd%20tucked%20aside%3A%20traveling%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZhuang%20didn't%20necessarily%20need%20to%20bring%20in%20any%20income%20while%20traveling%20%E2%80%94%20he'd%20budgeted%20enough%20to%20last%20a%20year%20%E2%80%94%20but%20he%20had%20the%20time%20and%20missed%20working%2C%20which%20led%20to%20his%20next%20side%20hustle%3A%20remote%20career%20coaching.%20Unlike%20e-commerce%2C%20coaching%20clicked%20for%20Zhuang%20and%2C%20%26quot%3Breally%20opened%20up%20my%20eyes%20to%20what's%20possible%20with%20a%20service%20kind%20of%20side%20hustle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2201a5c62b-e9ed-4ab3-97ff-620083b40294%5C%22%3ETransitioning%20to%20a%20'portfolio%20career'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EZhunag's%20travel%20sabbatical%20took%20him%20to%2020%20countries%20in%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20East%20Asia%2C%20Europe%2C%20and%20Latin%20America.%20On%20one%20of%20his%20trips%2C%20he%20met%20his%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20moved%20to%20Singapore%20in%202020%2C%20and%20Zhuang%20jumped%20back%20into%20the%20workforce.%20He%20worked%20for%20a%20fintech%20startup%20through%202023%2C%20at%20which%20point%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-strategy-coast-fire-financial-independence-retire-early-savings-investing-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehit%20Coast%20FIRE%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20quit%20to%20pursue%20what%20he%20calls%20a%20%26quot%3Bportfolio%20career.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20portfolio%20career%20involves%20multiple%20income%20streams.%20In%20its%20simplest%20form%2C%20it's%20a%20full-time%20job%20plus%20a%20side%20hustle%2C%20which%20Zhuang%20has%20technically%20been%20doing%20for%20years%3B%20for%20him%20currently%2C%20it%20means%20working%20on%20various%20side%20projects%20rather%20than%20having%20a%20full-time%20role%20with%20one%20employer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20revenue%20streams%20include%20three%20main%20categories%3A%20services%20such%20as%20consulting%20and%20advising%2C%20a%20cohort-based%20course%20that%20derived%20from%20his%20newsletter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneyabroad.co%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMoney%20Abroad%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20affiliates%20for%20various%20financial%20software%20and%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20his%20income%20streams%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20lucrative%20is%20the%20consulting%20and%20advising%20%E2%80%94%20the%20services%20piece%20%E2%80%94%20for%20sure%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e1458c3d-3b09-4427-b31b-38b2a5634e1f%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20make%20money%20with%20a%20service-based%20side%20hustle%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EZhuang%20has%20followed%20three%20principles%20to%20scale%20his%20coaching%20and%20consulting%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Start%20broad%20and%20niche%20down.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BNiching%20down%26quot%3B%20is%20fairly%20common%20advice%20in%20the%20business%20space%2C%20noted%20Zhuang%3B%20what%20often%20gets%20glossed%20over%20is%20%3Cem%3Ehow%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20niche%20down%2C%20which%20starts%20with%20fully%20understanding%20your%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20know%20exactly%20what%20all%20the%20niches%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20my%20experience%20consulting%20and%20coaching%2C%20I%20didn't%20know%20exactly%20about%20the%20market%20initially%20so%20I%20started%20out%20broad%20to%20test%20different%20hypotheses%20and%20learn%20about%20the%20market%20before%20narrowing%20my%20focus.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20broad%20market%20was%20Series%20A%20and%20B%20startups.%20After%20testing%20various%20industries%20within%20that%20space%2C%20over%20time%2C%20he%20found%20his%20niche%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20discovered%20that%2C%20generally%2C%20the%20type%20of%20companies%20that%20tend%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20me%20are%20fintech%20startups%20%E2%80%94%20those%20are%20ones%20where%20I%20add%20a%20lot%20of%20value.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221531%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22dexter%20zhuang%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6794075feb4be2fff9a2202a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221148%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZhuang's%20main%20revenue%20stream%20is%20coaching%20and%20consulting%2C%20which%20he%20can%20do%20remotely.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Dexter%20Zhuang%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Lean%20into%20your%20network%20to%20land%20your%20first%20client.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EZhuang%20said%20that%20his%20first%20three%20clients%20came%20from%20his%20network%3A%20%26quot%3BClient%20one%20was%20a%20referral%20from%20a%20VC%20friend%20of%20mine%2C%20client%20two%20was%20a%20referral%20from%20a%20colleague%20at%20work%2C%20client%20number%20three%20was%20someone%20in%20my%20direct%20network.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20fourth%20was%20his%20first%20inbound%20client%20%E2%80%94%20a%20founder%20who%20contacted%20him%20through%20his%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20definitely%20not%20just%20me%20that%20experiences%20this.%20I've%20interviewed%20over%2020%20other%20side%20hustlers%2C%20and%20what%20I%20discovered%20is%20that%20roughly%2050%25%20of%20them%20get%20their%20first%20client%20from%20referrals%20or%20their%20immediate%20network%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20that%20his%20data%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20statistically%20significant%20or%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20the%20point%20stands%3A%20%26quot%3BTap%20your%20referrals%20or%20your%20network%20for%20that%20first%20client.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Win%20'the%20game%20of%20one.'%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhen%20Zhuang%20first%20meets%20with%20clients%20looking%20to%20grow%20their%20side%20business%2C%20oftentimes%20he%20finds%20that%20they%20want%20to%20sell%20multiple%20products%20or%20services.%20He%20always%20advises%20them%20to%20%26quot%3Bwin%20the%20game%20of%20one%20offer%20first.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20validate%2C%20he%20explained%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20launch%20four%20offers%20and%20then%20it%20doesn't%20work%2C%20you%20may%20not%20have%20a%20clear%20idea%20of%20what's%20working%20and%20what's%20not.%20Whereas%2C%20if%20you%20just%20launch%20with%20one%20offer%2C%20then%20the%20validation%20is%20a%20lot%20easier%20because%20there's%20only%20one%20offer%20to%20accept%20or%20decline.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStart%20with%20what%20you%20think%20is%20your%20strongest%20product%2C%20test%20it%20on%20your%20first%20client%2C%20and%20then%20iterate%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThen%2C%20test%20that%20same%20offer%20with%20the%20second%20client%2C%20iterate%20it%2C%20then%20test%20it%20again%20with%20a%20third%20client%2C%20and%20iterate.%20The%20point%20is%20really%20on%20focusing%2C%20and%20resisting%20the%20temptation%20to%20add%20unnecessary%20complexity%20when%20you%20don't%20have%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-strategies-make-money-side-hustle-multiple-jobs-coaching-consulting-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737886921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679407f94bf52b7bab8a6cd0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-strategies-make-money-side-hustle-multiple-jobs-coaching-consulting-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20most%20effective%20way%20he's%20found%20to%20make%20money%20is%20through%20a%20se