0Republic%20Day%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737884600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsebi-launches-digital-knowledge-repository-dharohar-on-republic-day-125012600394_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20securities%20market%2C%20known%20for%20its%20diverse%20products%2C%20participants%2C%20and%20institutions%2C%20has%20a%20long-standing%20history%20of%20organised%20trading%20over%20the%20past%20150%20years%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Questions%20Gujarat%20Police%20Deployment%20In%20Delhi.%20Cops%20Clarify%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20former%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20claimed%20the%20Election%20Commission%20has%20removed%20Punjab%20Police%20and%20deployed%20Gujarat%20Police%20in%20the%20National%20Capital%20Territory%2C%20top%20sources%20in%20Delhi%20Police%20have%20provided%20a%20clarification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sources%20said%20220%20companies%20of%20security%20personnel%20were%20received%20in%20Delhi%2C%20including%20those%20from%20the%20CRPF%2C%20BSF%2C%20SSB%2C%20ITBP%2C%20CISF%20and%20RPF.%20Further%2C%2070%20companies%20were%20also%20deployed%20from%20Rajasthan%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Chandigarh%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20Police.%20These%20companies%20were%20received%20in%20Delhi%20in%20three%20phases%2C%20which%20included%20the%20deployment%20of%20seven%20to%20eight%20companies%20of%20Gujarat%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20clarified%20that%20the%20deployment%20came%20after%20250%20companies%20were%20demanded%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order%20as%20the%20February%205%20Assembly%20polls%20near.%20These%20companies%20will%20conduct%20tasks%20like%20flying%20squads%2C%20interstate%20border%20checking%2C%20area%20domination%2C%20and%20security%20at%20critical%20polling%20stations.%20Further%2C%20they%20will%20also%20serve%20at%20counting%20centres%20and%20as%20quick%20response%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20response%20was%20awaited%20from%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Police%2C%20with%20farmers'%20protest%20ongoing%20in%20the%20first%20two%20states%2C%20while%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20is%20ongoing%20in%20Prayagraj%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20raised%20questions%20on%20the%20deployment%20of%20eight%20companies%20of%20the%20State%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20(SRPF)%20from%20Gujarat.%20The%20SRPF%20companies%20reached%20Delhi%20on%20January%2013%20as%20per%20the%20order%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20(EC)%2C%20Commandant%20SRPF%2C%20Bhachau%2C%20Tejas%20Patel%20said%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunjab's%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20Gaurav%20Yadav%20said%20the%20state%20police%20component%20deployed%20for%20Kejriwal's%20security%20was%20withdrawn%20following%20directions%20from%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20and%20the%20Election%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGujarat%20Home%20Minister%20Harsh%20Sanghavi%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20hit%20back%20at%20Kejriwal%20over%20his%20lack%20of%20awareness%20regarding%20the%20poll%20body's%20norms.%20%26quot%3BNow%20I%20understand%20why%20people%20call%20you%20a%20fraud.%20Kejriwal%20ji%2C%20as%20a%20former%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20I'm%20surprised%20you're%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission's%20norms%2C%26quot%3B%20Sanghavi%20stated%20in%20his%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey've%20requested%20forces%20from%20various%20states%2C%20not%20just%20Gujarat.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20has%20ordered%20SRP%20deployment%20from%20various%20states%2C%20a%20routine%20procedure.%20As%20per%20their%20request%2C%208%20companies%20of%20SRP%20from%20Gujarat%20were%20sent%20to%20Delhi%20for%20the%20scheduled%20election%20on%2011%2F1%2F25.%20Why%20the%20selective%20mention%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20Kejriwal%20ji%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolling%20for%20all%2070%20assembly%20seats%20in%20Delhi%20will%20be%20held%20on%20February%205%20and%20the%20votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20February%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737884340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fqv6d9sn8_arvind-kejriwal-_625x300_22_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-questions-gujarat-police-deployment-in-delhi-cops-react-7563174%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shortly%20after%20former%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20claimed%20the%20Election%20Commission%20has%20removed%20Punjab%20Police%20and%20deployed%20Gujarat%20Police%20in%20the%20National%20Capital%20Territory%2C%20top%20sources%20in%20Delhi%20Police%20debunked%20the%20claim.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-questions-gujarat-police-deployment-in-delhi-cops-react-7563174%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tableaux%20Focus%20On%20Development%2C%20Nari%20Shakti%20As%20India%20Celebrates%20Republic%20Day%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20celebrated%20its%2076th%20Republic%20Day%20focusing%20on%2075%20years%20of%20enactment%20of%20the%20Constitution%20and%20Jan%20Bhagidari%20(public%20movement).%20The%20celebrations%20witnessed%20a%20blend%20of%20India's%20rich%20cultural%20diversity%2C%20unity%2C%20equality%2C%20development%20and%20military%20prowess.%20Apart%20from%20Indonesian%20President%20Prabowo%20Subianto%2C%20who%20is%20the%20chief%20guest%2C%2010%2C000%20special%20guests%20were%20in%20attendance.%20These%20guests%20are%20called%20the%20architects%20of%20'Swarnim%20Bharat'%20(golden%20India).%20They%20include%20the%20best%20performers%20in%20various%20fields%20and%20