RDAI%2C%20questioning%20celebrities'%20%26quot%3Bpreferential%20treatment%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20knife%20attack%20on%20Mr%20Khan%20during%20a%20burglary%20attempt%20at%20his%20Mumbai%20home%2C%20a%20document%20of%20his%20mediclaim%20approval%20emerged%20on%20social%20media.%20According%20to%20the%20document%2C%20a%20cashless%20request%20of%20nearly%20Rs%2036%20lakh%20had%20been%20placed%20for%20the%20actor's%20five-day%20stay.%20In%20its%20initial%20approval%2C%20the%20insurance%20provider%20had%20cleared%20a%20payout%20of%20Rs%2025%20lakh.%20Niva%20Bupa%20confirmed%20receiving%20the%20pre-authorisation%20request%20and%20said%20further%20claims%20would%20be%20processed%20as%20per%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mumbai-based%20Association%20of%20Medical%20Consultants%2C%20which%20says%20it%20represents%20over%2014%2C000%20medical%20practitioners%20and%20has%20branches%20in%20several%20cities%2C%20has%20written%20to%20the%20chairman%20of%20IRDAI%20--%20Insurance%20Regulatory%20and%20Development%20Authority%20of%20India%20--%20on%20the%20cashless%20clearance%20for%20Mr%20Khan's%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20writing%20to%20express%20our%20concern%20and%20dissatisfaction%20regarding%20the%20recent%20news%20of%20Mr%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20being%20sanctioned%20Rs%2025%20lakhs%20for%20cashless%20treatment%20under%20his%20insurance%20policy%2C%20which%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20preferential%20treatment%20compared%20to%20the%20benefits%20available%20to%20the%20common%20policyholders%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20organisation%20has%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20instance%20highlights%20a%20troubling%20trend%20where%20celebrities%20and%20high-profile%20individuals%20and%20patients%20with%20corporate%20policies%20receive%20favorable%20terms%20and%20higher%20cashless%20treatment%20limits%2C%20while%20ordinary%20citizens%20struggle%20with%20insufficient%20coverage%20and%20low%20reimbursement%20rates%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Association%20of%20Medical%20Consultants%20has%20said%20such%20practices%20create%20an%20%26quot%3Bunfair%20disparity%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20Insurance%20should%20be%20a%20safeguard%20for%20all%2C%20irrespective%20of%20social%20status.%20Preferential%20treatment%20based%20on%20celebrity%20status%20creates%20a%20two-tier%20system%2C%20which%20is%20discriminatory%20against%20ordinary%20policyholders.%20There%20is%20a%20need%20for%20greater%20transparency%20in%20how%20insurance%20claims%20and%20cashless%20treatment%20limits%20are%20determined%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20has%20requested%20IRDAI%20to%20probe%20the%20matter%20and%20ensure%20that%20all%20policyholders%2C%20regardless%20of%20social%20status%2C%20are%20treated%C2%A0equally.%20It%20has%20also%20demanded%20guidelines%20to%20prevent%20preferential%20treatment%20and%20enhance%20transparency%20in%20mediclaim%20approvals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khan%20was%20admitted%20to%20Mumbai's%20Lilavati%20Hospital%20on%20January%2016%20after%20he%20suffered%20six%20stab%20injuries%20during%20a%20fight%20with%20an%20intruder%20who%20had%20broken%20into%20his%20home%20to%20commit%20robbery.%20One%20of%20his%20injuries%20was%20on%20the%20spine%20and%20the%20knife%20missed%20his%20spinal%20cord%20by%20just%202%20mm%2C%20doctors%20have%20said.%20Mr%20Khan%20has%20been%20operated%20upon%20for%20his%20back%20injury%20and%20wounds%20on%20his%20arm%20and%20neck.%20He%20was%20discharged%20last%20week%20and%20has%20been%20advised%20bed%20rest%20for%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737883380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fti7q3jpg_saif-ali-khan-stabbed-_650x400_24_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsaif-ali-khan-attacked-unfair-disparity-doctors-body-to-insurance-regulator-after-saif-attack-7562671%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Days%20aft