0During%20a%20memorable%20appearance%20on%20Kareena's%20radio%20show%20last%20year%2C%20Saif%20shared%20a%20significant%20piece%20of%20advice%20he%20received%20from%20his%20close%20friend%2C%20Rani%20Mukerji%2C%20which%20proved%20invaluable%20as%20he%20navigated%20his%20relationship%20with%20Kareena%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20UP%20Tableau%20At%20Republic%20Day%20Parade%20Celebrates%20Maha%20Kumbh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20depictions%20of%20'Samudra%20Manthan'%2C%20'Amrit%20Kalash'%20and%20holy%20men%20bathing%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20Sangam%2C%20the%20Republic%20Day%20tableau%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20celebrated%20the%20ongoing%20Maha%20Kumbh%20in%20Prayagraj%20and%20showcased%20a%20metaphorical%20confluence%20of%20'virasat'%20and%20'vikas'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tableau%20drew%20cheers%20from%20the%20crowd%20as%20it%20rolled%20down%20the%20Kartavya%20Path%20here%20during%20the%20ceremonial%20parade%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBilled%20as%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20gatherings%20of%20humanity%20on%20earth%2C%20Maha%20Kumbh%202025%20began%20on%20January%2013%20and%20will%20culminate%20on%20February%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%2075%20years%20of%20enactment%20of%20the%20Constitution%20is%20the%20focus%20of%2076th%20Republic%20Day%20celebrations%2C%20the%20theme%20for%20the%20tableaux%20is%20'Swarnim%20Bharat%3A%20Virasat%20aur%20Vikas'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tableau%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20showcases%20the%20grandeur%20of%20Maha%20Kumbh%202025%2C%20portraying%20a%20metaphorical%20'Sangam'%20of%20'virasat'%20and%20'vikas'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeading%20the%20display%20is%20an%20impressive%20replica%20of%20the%20'Amrit%20Kalash'%20tilted%20forward%2C%20symbolising%20the%20flow%20of%20the%20sacred%20'Amritdhara'.%20Surrounding%20it%2C%20seers%20and%20saints%20have%20been%20depicted%20blowing%20conch%20shells%2C%20performing%20'snan'%20at%20Sangam%2C%20and%20engaging%20in%20meditation%2C%20while%20devotees%20immerse%20themselves%20in%20the%20holy%20waters%20of%20the%20confluence%20of%20Ganga%2C%20Yamuna%20and%20the%20mythical%20Saraswati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20panel%20of%20the%20trailer%2C%20the%20'akharas'%2C%20and%20devotees%20going%20for%20the%20'Amrit%20snan'%20are%20depicted%20through%20murals%20and%20LED%20screens%2C%20according%20to%20a%20description%20of%20the%20tableau%20shared%20by%20Defence%20Ministry%20officials%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20its%20core%2C%20the%20mythical%20tale%20of%20'Samudra%20Manthan'%20has%20been%20vividly%20depicted%2C%20symbolising%20the%20profound%20historical%20and%20cultural%20significance%20of%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh.%20On%20its%20back%20side%2C%2014%20gems%20that%20emerged%20from%20the%20churning%20of%20the%20ocean%2C%20have%20been%20depicted%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20honour%20and%20great%20pride%20that%20Maha%20Kumbh%2C%20our%20great%20heritage%20will%20be%20showcased%20on%20Kartavya%20Path%20while%20the%20religious%20gathering%20is%20currently%20underway%20in%20Prayagraj%2C%26quot%3B%20Ram%20Manohar%20Tripathi%2C%20deputy%20director%20in%20the%20Department%20of%20Information%20%26amp%3B%20Public%20Relations%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20said%20on%20January%2022%2C%20during%20a%20preview%20of%20the%20Republic%20Day%20tableau%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20depictions%20of%20'Samudra%20Manthan'%2C%20'Amrit%20Kalash'%20and%20holy%20men%20bathing%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20confluence%2C%20people%20will%20get%20a%20feel%20of%20'Sangam'%20during%20the%20Republic%20Day%20Parade.%20And%2C%20this%20tableau%20also%20depicts%20various%20development%20initiatives%20of%20the%20UP%20government%2C%20thus%20it%20is%20sort%20of%20a%20'sangam'%20of%20'virasat'%20and%20'vikas'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20troupe%20of%20artistes%20dressed%20in%20traditional%20attire%20walked%20while%20another%20person%20blew%20a%20conch%20and%20a%20few%20others%20played%20'damru'%2C%20walking%20along%20side%20the%20state%20tableau.%20The%20Maha%20Kumbh%20is%20held%20every%2012%20years%20in%20Prayagraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20robust%20technological%20and%20digital%20preparations%20for%20Maha%20Kumbh%2C%20the%20tableau%20also%20showcases%20the%20state-of-the-art%20Integrated%20Command%20and%20Control%20Center%20(ICCC)%20for%20efficient%20security%20and%20crowd%20management%20at%20the%20Kumbh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737875580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fjgn8i8qo_up-tableau_625x300_26_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-up-tableau-at-republic-day-parade-celebrates-maha-kumbh-7562148%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Republic%20Day%20tableau%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20celebrated%20the%20ongoing%20Maha%20Kumbh%20in%20Prayagraj.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-up-tableau-at-republic-day-parade-celebrates-maha-kumbh-7562148%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225%2C000%20artists%2C%2045%20dance%20forms%3A%20Performances%20cover%20Kartavya%20Path%20on%20R-Day%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737875286000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2F5-000-artists-45-dance-forms-performances-cover-kartavya-path-on-r-day-125012600244_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20performance%20covered%20the%20entire%20Kartavya%20Path%20from%20Vijay%20Chowk%20and%20C%20hex