ised%20representatives%20are%20permitted%20to%20accompany%20the%20polling%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CEO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poll%20body%20said%20the%20'vote-from-home'%20exercise%20uses%20the%20ballot%20voting%20method.%20%26quot%3BThe%20team%20will%20provide%20the%20voter%20with%20a%20ballot%20paper%20and%20ensure%20the%20voting%20process%20is%20conducted%20confidentially%20and%20transparently%20as%20per%20the%20prescribed%20guidelines%20pr%20ECI%20in%20this%20reference.%20The%20entire%20process%20will%20be%20videographed%20to%20maintain%20transparency.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20clarify%20again%2C%20Voters%20who%20opt%20for%20this%20Home%20Voting%20facility%20will%20not%20be%20permitted%20to%20vote%20at%20polling%20stations%20on%20election%20day%20also%20this%20Home%20voting%20option%20is%20voluntary.%20To%20submit%2C%20it%20is%20to%20highlight%20that%20this%20initiative%20marks%20a%20significant%20step%20towards%20inclusive%20voting%2C%20ensuring%20that%20senior%20citizens%20and%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20can%20participate%20in%20the%20electoral%20process%20with%20greater%20ease%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Delhi%20CEO's%20office%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBesides%20all%20the%20National%20and%20local%20newspapers%20have%20covered%20the%20Home%20voting%20extensively.%20Again%20we%20are%20committed%20to%20follow%20all%20the%20guidelines%20of%20ECI%20to%20conduct%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20election.%20Further%2C%20in%20case%20of%20any%20issue%2C%20the%20voter%20is%20requested%20to%20visit%20the%20local%20RO%2F%20DEO%20office%20or%20call%20our%20centralized%20helpline%20no%201950%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737874920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F8dk2e97o_delhi-election-_625x300_26_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-election-2025-aaps-big-charge-on-vote-from-home-for-elderly-poll-bodys-response-7562290%22%2C