-year-old%20envisioned%20the%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20constructed%20over%20an%20area%20of%202%2C7%20acres%20in%20the%20traditional%20Nagar%20style%20without%20using%20iron.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sompura%20is%20the%20grandson%20of%20Padma%20Shri%20Prabhashankarbhai%20Oghadbhai%20Somapura%2C%20whom%20he%20also%20considers%20his%20teacher.%20As%20per%20his%20website%2C%20he%20was%20awarded%20Best%20Architect%20Of%20The%20Year%201997%20award%20and%20his%20creation%20of%20Shri%20Akshar%20Purshottam%20Swaminarayan%20Temple%20at%20London%20was%20recognised%20by%20the%20Guiness%20Book%20of%20World%20Records.%20Further%2C%20he%20created%20the%20Akshardham%20temple%20in%20Gujarat's%20Gandhinagar%2C%20108%20Bhaktivihar%2C%20and%20temples%20in%20Singapore%20and%20USA%2C%20all%20of%20which%20received%20widespread%20appreciation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737864780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fr6e314vo_chandrakant-sompura-ram-temple_625x300_19_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhya-ram-temple-architect-chandrakant-somapura-to-be-conferred-with-padma-shri-7561325%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chandrakant%20Sompura%2C%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Ayodhya%2C%20is%20among%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20recipients%20this%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhya-ram-temple-architect-chandrakant-somapura-to-be-conferred-with-padma-shri-7561325%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Box%20Office%3A%20Akshay%20Kumar's%20Sky%20Force%20Shows%20No%20Signs%20Of%20Slowing%20Down%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fsky-force-box-office-collection-day-1-akshay-kumars-big-comeback-with-double-digit-opening-after-a-string-of-flops-7554142%5C%22%3EAkshay%20Kumar%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fsky-force-box-office-collection-day-1-akshay-kumars-big-comeback-with-double-digit-opening-after-a-string-of-flops-7554142%5C%22%3EVeer%20Pahariya%3C%2Fa%3E's%20aerial%20action%20thriller%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fsky-force-box-office-collection-day-1-akshay-kumars-big-comeback-with-double-digit-opening-after-a-string-of-flops-7554142%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESky%20Force%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20experienced%20a%2075%25%20surge%20in%20earnings%20on%20Saturday%2C%20following%20a%20solid%20opening%20day%20at%20the%20box%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20reported%20by%20Sacnilk%2C%20the%20film%20saw%20a%2075.51%25%20increase%20in%20earnings%2C%20raking%20in%20Rs%2021.5%20crore%20on%20Saturday%20alone.%20This%20brings%20its%20total%20earnings%20to%20Rs%2033.75%20crore%20after%20two%20days%20of%20release.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fsky-force-advance-booking-update-akshay-kumar-and-veer-pahariyas-film-sells-over-64-000-tickets-earns-rs-1-54-crore-7538499%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESky%20Force%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20come%20as%20a%20much-needed%20relief%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fsky-force-advance-booking-update-akshay-kumar-and-veer-pahariyas-film-sells-over-64-000-tickets-earns-rs-1-54-crore-7538499%5C%22%3EAkshay%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20marking%20his%20most%20successful%20movie%20release%20in%20years.%20The%20film%20opened%20to%20solid%20double-digit%20collections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Sacnilk%2C%20%3Cem%3ESky%20Force%3C%2Fem%3E%20earned%20Rs%2011.25%20crore%20(net)%20on%20its%20opening%20day.%20The%20movie%20was%20made%20on%20a%20relatively%20modest%20budget%20of%20Rs%20160%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20big%20hit%20in%20Akshay%20Kumar's%20career%20was%20%3Cem%3ESooryavanshi%20(2021)%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20directed%20by%20Rohit%20Shetty.%20It%20was%20made%20on%20a%20budget%20of%20Rs%20160%20crore%20and%20earned%20Rs%20293%20crore%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20last%20few%20releases%2C%20including%20%3Cem%3EKhel%20Khel%20Mein%2C%20Sarfira%2C%20Bade%20Miyan%20Chote%20Miyan%2C%20Mission%20Raniganj%2C%20Selfiee%2C%20Ram%20Setu%2C%20Raksha%20Bandhan%2C%20Samrat%20Prithviraj%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3EBachchhan%20Paandey%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20all%20failed%20to%20make%20a%20mark%20at%20the%20box%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkshay's%20last%20major%20release%2C%20%3Cem%3ESingham%20Again%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20raked%20in%20Rs%20372.4%20crore%20globally%2C%20but%20that%20movie%20was%20led%20by%20Ajay%20Devgn%20and%20featured%20an%20ensemble%20cast%2C%20with%20Akshay%20appearing%20in%20a%20cameo.%20Additionally%2C%20he%20made%20a%20guest%20appearance%20in%20%3Cem%3EStree%202%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20performed%20well%2C%20earning%20Rs%20857.15%20crore%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20film's%20trailer%20launch%2C%20%3Cem%3ESky%20Force%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20drawn%20comparisons%20to%20%3Cem%3EFighter%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20stars%20Hrithik%20Roshan%20and%20Deepika%20Padukone.%20%3Cem%3EFighter%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20also%20released%20around%20Republic%20Day%20last%20year%20and%20made%20Rs%2022.5%20crore%20on%20its%20opening%20day.%20Fighter%2C%20with%20a%20production%20budget%20of%20Rs%20250%20crore%2C%20went%20on%20to%20become%20a%20success%2C%20grossing%20Rs%20358.83%20crore%20worldwide.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESky%20Force%20is%20based%20on%20the%20untold%20story%20of%20India's%20first%20and%20deadliest%20airstrike%2C%20showcasing%20the%20events%20of%20the%201965%20India-Pakistan%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVeer%20Pahariya%20makes%20his%20acting%20debut%20as%20IAF%20officer%20T%20Vijaya%2C%20who%20goes%20missing%20in%20action%20during%20the%20war%2C%20while%20Akshay%20Kumar%20plays%20his%20fellow%20officer%2C%20KO%20Ahuja%2C%20who%20embarks%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20find%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20also%20featu